headline.main: ALLIES MOPPING UP FOE AT MILNE BAY; Japanese Planes Strike at Airfield There -- 3 Enemy Tanks in Area Destroyed

lead_paragraph: AT UNITED NATIONS HEADQUARTERS, Australia, Tuesday, Sept. 1 -- The Milne Bay battle has progressed to the point where today's communique from General Douglas MacArthur's headquarters speaks of it as a "mopping up" operation.
abstract: Allies reptd mopping up, Milne Bay area, New Guinea
